un tsufelik hot men im ongenumen, far dem s'iz gevezn

72
00:04:50,598 --> 00:04:53,867
a ongezeene yid hot gehat di fabrik,

73
00:04:54,142 --> 00:04:56,314
dortn hobn gearbet polyakn,

74
00:04:56,387 --> 00:04:58,991
hot men zey oykhet gegebn gelt

75
