ikh bin ts- eyn molt kum ikh tsurik, oyf der nakht, aheym,

215
00:13:38,398 --> 00:13:40,013
lozt men mikh nisht arayn.

216
00:13:40,203 --> 00:13:44,901
ikh hob a sh- shtendik a shlisl fun undzer hoyz!

217
00:13:44,901 --> 00:13:49,699
un s'iz DOZORCA, un er geyt tsu, un ikh zog ver s'iz!

218
00:13:50,025 --> 00:13:51,573
un er makht mir nisht oyf!

219
00:13:52,168 --> 00:13:55,430
zog ikh im ver ikh bin! ikh bin aheymgekumen!

220
00:13:55,430 --> 00:13:57,616
ikh bin di baleboste fun hoyz!

221
00:13:57,616 --> 00:13:59,436
du arbetst bay undz!

222
00:13:59,778 --> 00:14:01,477
zogt er, "neyn,

223
00:14:02,276 --> 00:14:04,330
do voynt ets shoyn nisht."

224
00:14:05,212 --> 00:14:06,827
ikh hob nisht farshtanen.

225
00:14:09,380 --> 00:14:11,470
undz hot men gevoynt in der heykh,

226
00:14:11,470 --> 00:14:15,351
un huntn hot gevoynt a yidishe mishpokhe,

227
00:14:15,351 --> 00:14:18,302
un zey hobn gehert, un zey hobn gevust!

228
00:14:19,674 --> 00:14:23,179
zey hobn oyfgemakht dos fentster, aroysgeshtelt mir a shtul,

229
00:14:23,387 --> 00:14:25,441
un ikh bin arayngeganen tsu zey,

230
00:14:25,968 --> 00:14:31,212
un ikh hob bay zey genakhtikt, un zey hobn mir fartseylt az

231
00:14:33,208 --> 00:14:36,409
avade der zelber vos hot mir nisht gevolt oyfmakhn,

232
00:14:37,224 --> 00:14:40,965
hot gezogt az se voynen bay undz gest,

233
00:14:41,190 --> 00:14:42,451
men iz raykh,

234
00:14:46,404 --> 00:14:49,000
un zey zenen gekumen arayn,

235
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:52,896
in der fri, di daytshn, ikh bin nisht gevezn in der heym,

236
00:14:53,087 --> 00:14:58,482
zey hobn genumen dem tateshi, mameshi, mit mayne tsvey brider,

237
00:14:58,757 --> 00:15:02,346
in der fri, zey hobn zikh koym ongetun,

238
00:15:03,330 --> 00:15:05,721
gornisht gelozt mitnemen,

239
00:15:06,097 --> 00:15:08,741
der tateshi afilet on bril,

240
00:15:10,299 --> 00:15:14,310
un aroy- di mameshi hot gevolt nemen broyt mit puter

241
00:15:15,311 --> 00:15:16,977
hobn zey nisht gelozt,

242
00:15:18,939 --> 00:15:22,140
un me hot zey gefirt in magistrat,

243
00:15:23,597 --> 00:15:25,499
me hot gevoynt nisht vayt,

244
00:15:26,381 --> 00:15:29,650
un me hot zey dort gehaltn in keler,

245
00:15:32,017 --> 00:15:33,868
dos hot men mir fartseylt.

246
00:15:35,612 --> 00:15:37,733
ikh bin geven dokh fray,

247
00:15:37,923 --> 00:15:40,291
ikh hob shoyn nisht gehat vu tsu voynen,

248
00:15:40,291 --> 00:15:42,171
ober ikh hob gehat,

249
00:15:44,268 --> 00:15:48,178
f- ikh hob gehat di do vos se zey hobn geblibn.

250
00:15:49,635 --> 00:15:52,990
bin ikh geganen, ikh hob gevolt epes gebn tsu esn,

251
00:15:52,990 --> 00:15:54,726
s'iz geven ales farmakht.

252
00:15:55,001 --> 00:15:57,865
un zey zenen huntn gevezn, in keler,

253
00:16:01,413 --> 00:16:03,334
un me hot dervayl ongehoybn,

254
00:16:03,334 --> 00:16:07,365
se hot gedoyert tsvey vokhn, mer,

255
00:16:09,058 --> 00:16:13,002
un ikh hob gekrign brivelekh, hot mir emetser gebrengt.

256
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:15,937
ikh zol mikh nisht zorgn, nebekh.

257
00:16:16,331 --> 00:16:21,889
un me hot ongehoybn dernokh eyntsele raykhe mentshn aroysnemen

258
00:16:21,889 --> 00:16:24,139
fun andere voynungen. yidn.

259
00:16:24,887 --> 00:16:28,037
nor raykhe hot men gezukht.

260
00:16:29,527 --> 00:16:33,319
un me hot nisht gehat keyn plats inem magistrat,

261
00:16:33,493 --> 00:16:38,460
zenen zey oyfgemakht HALA TARGOWA

262
00:16:38,460 --> 00:16:45,165
a plats vos s'iz vos s'iz geven amolt ferd, dernokh hobn mentshn, oreme, farkoyft zeyere zakhn

263
00:16:45,491 --> 00:16:47,403
iz gevezn aza groys hoyz,

264
00:16:47,403 --> 00:16:49,732
vos hot hot geheysn HALA TARGOWA,

265
00:16:49,732 --> 00:16:52,202
hot men di yidn dortn arayngefirt,

266
00:16:53,456 --> 00:16:57,990
un zey hobn geshlofn oyf der erd vos se hot zikh, zey hobn zikh untergeleygt.

267
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:01,889
un undz ze'mir fun dem gevor gevorn,

268
00:17:03,176 --> 00:17:04,892
az zey zenen dortn,

269
00:17:05,235 --> 00:17:10,107
hob ikh mikh oykhet arayngenart tsu zayn in eynem mit mayne eltern.

270
00:17:10,635 --> 00:17:19,354
hob ikh f- gehert un gezen az mayn eltere bruder iz gevezn in gantsn shvarts.

271
00:17:19,578 --> 00:17:23,876
far hakn. me hot geshlogn. yedern tog.

272
00:17:25,653 --> 00:17:27,794
vu me hot ales,

273
00:17:27,794 --> 00:17:31,329
un puter hot me-, hot di mameshi gevolt brengen!

274
00:17:31,329 --> 00:17:34,069
"vu hostu di puter?" un azoy vayter,

275
00:17:34,918 --> 00:17:38,796
un yetst bin ikh shoyn gevezn mit mayn mameshi mitn tateshi,

276
00:17:38,796 --> 00:17:42,894
mit di brider, un mit nokh yidn in di HALA

277
00:17:43,237 --> 00:17:44,751
un dortn geshlofn.

278
00:17:46,258 --> 00:17:49,358
mayn mameshi mitn tateshi hobn gezogt, "neyn,

279
00:17:49,413 --> 00:17:51,382
undz tor'mir do nisht blaybn."

280
00:17:51,928 --> 00:17:52,902
me zol,

281
00:17:53,210 --> 00:17:57,863
"koydem geyts tsu undzere bakante shlofn oyf di PIŁSUDSKIEGO."

282
00:17:57,902 --> 00:17:59,939
hobn zey gegebn dem shlisl.

283
00:18:01,428 --> 00:18:06,571
un dos tsveyte, "ets muzt antloyfn, nokh Rusland."

284
00:18:07,149 --> 00:18:12,510
far dem, mit vos se vet mit undz zayn, gloybt men nisht.

285
00:18:13,612 --> 00:18:18,096
zey hobn nisht gehat, zey hobn nisht gegloybt di daytshn.

286
00:18:19,721 --> 00:18:26,196
ze'mir geganen me zol voynen, ikh mit mayn bruder, in di shtot nokh,

287
00:18:26,370 --> 00:18:29,352
ze'mir arayngeganen oyf der nakht in a voynung,

288
00:18:29,475 --> 00:18:34,043
vos keyner iz nisht gevezn, di mentshn zenen gevezn ikh veys nisht vu,

289
00:18:34,098 --> 00:18:37,758
ober antlofn nokh Rusland, ober in di HALA,

290
00:18:37,758 --> 00:18:39,612
me hot gekrign fun di eltern.

291
00:18:39,853 --> 00:18:43,830
un dortn hot men gevolt, hot men gezen s'iz ales,

292
00:18:43,987 --> 00:18:46,828
gants vertshaft iz do gornisht gerirt!

293
00:18:46,828 --> 00:18:48,876
gornisht mitgenumen mit zikh!

294
00:18:49,269 --> 00:18:50,962
un s'iz a, do a kukh!

295
00:18:50,962 --> 00:18:54,377
hob ikh gevolt opkokhn epes varemes,

296
00:18:54,534 --> 00:18:58,646
vaser hob ikh gemakht un, un di kukh, fayer.

297
00:18:59,951 --> 00:19:05,043
un me hot, m'iz gevezn efsher a sho, hekhstns,

298
00:19:05,182 --> 00:19:08,603
un di sht- in di voynung, s'iz shoyn geven oyf der nakht, shpet,

299
00:19:09,772 --> 00:19:12,613
to, klapt men, me hert, me geyt,

300
00:19:12,613 --> 00:19:18,503
un men klapt mit di kolbes, mit di tsveyter zayt fun di biksn, in di tir!

301
00:19:18,503 --> 00:19:20,230
"RAUS! RAUS!"

302
00:19:20,758 --> 00:19:26,760
iz gevezn tsvey GESTAPOWTSES, mit di biksn, ober, ober zelner,

303
00:19:27,828 --> 00:19:28,954
"aroys!"

304
00:19:30,090 --> 00:19:33,656
me zol mitnemen dos gold, mit mit tayere zakhn,

305
00:19:33,656 --> 00:19:37,190
undz hot men dortn gornisht gehat, far dem me iz ersht gekumen!

306
00:19:37,413 --> 00:19:40,109
yo, ze'mir geganen. mit zey.

307
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,774
m'iz aroysgekumen in di gas arayn,

308
00:19:42,847 --> 00:19:46,183
s'iz geven bay der nakht, tsene, eleve oyf der nakht,

309
00:19:46,543 --> 00:19:53,906
hot men gezen oyfn tretuar, nisht tretuar, di KVISH, di shosey,

310
00:19:53,906 --> 00:19:58,266
di di vi di AUTOS forn, vi heyst es?

311
00:19:58,355 --> 00:20:01,236
hot men gezen laylekher oysgeleygt.

312
00:20:01,545 --> 00:20:06,838
laylekher. oysgeleygt di gantse veg vays. yo.

313
00:20:07,856 --> 00:20:11,549
di gantse veg iz vays, mit laylekher oysgeleygt,

314
00:20:11,549 --> 00:20:16,069
un fun di zayt shteyen yidn, un fun di zayt shteyen yidn.

315
00:20:17,323 --> 00:20:21,705
bay di laylekher. un me hot geshtanen un gevart!

316
00:20:23,499 --> 00:20:29,113
s'iz geven kil. ikh gedenk nisht sara monat. ikh veys nisht vos!

317
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:32,744
un me hot gevart.

318
00:20:32,744 --> 00:20:37,871
s'iz shoyn k-, ongekumen a sakh yidn fun beyde zaytn,

319
00:20:38,113 --> 00:20:40,506
hobn zey geshrign, di daytshn,

320
00:20:40,506 --> 00:20:43,254
"aroysnemen fun di tashn dos gold,

321
00:20:43,513 --> 00:20:48,379
ales gold, vos me hot nor, tayere zakhn,

322
00:20:48,379 --> 00:20:49,880
zol men do aroysleygn,"

323
00:20:49,880 --> 00:20:53,329
un az nisht veln zey bald shisn, undz vel'mir zen.

324
00:20:53,705 --> 00:20:55,978
me vet keyn eyn mentsh nisht iberlozn!

325
00:21:00,708 --> 00:21:04,984
ikh hob genumen dos zeygerl, ikh hob genumen di fingerlekh,

326
00:21:04,984 --> 00:21:07,994
gehat tsvey fingerlekh, di bruder oykhet UNK,

327
00:21:08,657 --> 00:21:12,617
un me hot es anidergevorfn oyfn laylekh.

328
00:21:12,757 --> 00:21:15,047
andere hobn dos zelbe getun.

329
00:21:18,039 --> 00:21:21,088
di protsesye hot gedoyert efsher tsvey sho.

330
00:21:22,764 --> 00:21:27,974
un dernokh hobn zey undz arayngefirt tsurik in di HALA,

331
00:21:28,788 --> 00:21:31,620
di HALA TARGOWA. yene zenen nokh nisht gevezn,

332
00:21:31,620 --> 00:21:34,909
undz ze'mir tsurikgeganen tsu, tsu di eltern,

333
00:21:35,049 --> 00:21:37,390
tsu di mayn mameshi mitn tateshi.

334
00:21:38,677 --> 00:21:43,971
hobn zey gezogt, "mer nisht! ets muzt antloyfn!"

335
00:21:43,993 --> 00:21:46,707
ikh bin gevezn, mit mayn bruder.

336
00:21:46,707 --> 00:21:52,813
un der kleyner bruder vet blaybn mit zey, un er hot nisht gevolt

337
00:21:53,747 --> 00:21:58,500
undz zol'mir loyfn nokh Rusland far dem s'iz do keyn plats nisht.

338
00:22:00,902 --> 00:22:07,748
densmolt iz shoyn gevezn opaskes, vayse. ARMbender.

339
00:22:10,757 --> 00:22:12,642
ken zayn bay andere.

340
00:22:13,676 --> 00:22:20,269
nor ikh, a, vos ikh hob gehat mayn tateshi, vos er hot nisht gegleybt az gornisht vet undz helfn,

341
00:22:20,291 --> 00:22:24,538
hob hob keyn pas- opaske nisht ongetun di gantse krig.

342
00:22:26,467 --> 00:22:29,786
ober tomer me khapt dikh, vest es nisht hobn?

343
00:22:30,197 --> 00:22:31,637
vet men dikh shisn!

344
00:22:31,637 --> 00:22:33,718
hob ikh gehaltn dos in di tash.

345
00:22:34,938 --> 00:22:39,321
ober dernokh, nokh a tsayt, nokh a halb yor,

346
00:22:39,528 --> 00:22:45,763
hob ikh mikh meyashev gevezn az me vet mikh khapn, un me vet mir gefinen, vet dokh nokh erger zayn!

347
00:22:45,814 --> 00:22:47,972
un ikh ⟨genar⟩ un me gefint!

348
00:22:47,972 --> 00:22:51,994
hob ikh in gantsn nisht gehat keyn opaske. un mayn bruder oykh nisht.

349
00:22:53,265 --> 00:23:01,816
mit a opaske hot men nisht gekent aroyfgeyn oyf keyn ban, oyf a tsug, zey farshteyen.

350
00:23:03,035 --> 00:23:07,756
ober on opaske, ze'mir dokh nisht keyn yidn, ken men forn!

351
00:23:08,165 --> 00:23:10,151
ze'mir geforn nokh Lodzh.

352
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:14,607
un gekumen tsu mayne mishpokhe,

353
00:23:15,624 --> 00:23:18,943
zogn zey, "ets vilts forn nokh Rusland?"

354
00:23:19,151 --> 00:23:21,205
ikh, undz vet men nisht lozn.

355
00:23:22,374 --> 00:23:26,740
undz ze'mir azelkhe, ikh bin aza delikat kind! mayn bruder!

356
00:23:27,133 --> 00:23:33,726
nokh Rusland forn nor shtarke, gezunte, vos zey kenen arbetn shver!

357
00:23:34,271 --> 00:23:38,181
undz vet men forn mit zey. nokh Varshe.

358
00:23:41,088 --> 00:23:44,120
un zey kenen zikh shikeven nokh Varshe,

359
00:23:45,729 --> 00:23:54,347
un dervayl, shikt mikh di kuzin vos hot gevoynt UNK

360
00:23:54,386 --> 00:23:56,828
zi iz geven Nadel fun der heym.

361
00:23:57,221 --> 00:24:06,210
er geyt mit a opaske un un er un men past oyf im oyf far dem er iz a raykher mentsh.

362
00:24:06,570 --> 00:24:12,100
oyb ikh vil n'im epes tun, gey in di bank arayn. zog ikh, "far vos nisht!"

363
00:24:12,408 --> 00:24:22,157
zogt er, "ober on opaske ken men dikh epes tun. muzst ontun a opaske.

364
00:24:22,770 --> 00:24:27,591
do hostu. un az nisht iz ⟨mayn vort⟩ vil ikh nisht du zolst geyn."

365
00:24:28,018 --> 00:24:31,474
ikh hob gevolt far n'im geyn, hob ikh ongetun di opaske,

366
00:24:31,474 --> 00:24:35,898
azoy vi ikh bin aroysgeganen hot men mikh genumen tsu di arbet oyf a gantse tog.

367
00:24:35,898 --> 00:24:39,859
yo. ikh bin nor aroysgeganen. ikh bin shoyn nisht geshtanen dortn.

368
00:24:40,488 --> 00:24:43,268
⟨un oyf⟩ gelt, in di bank.

369
00:24:43,475 --> 00:24:47,236
hob ikh a gantsn tog gearbet. aza an arbet, a shvere,

370
00:24:47,236 --> 00:24:49,697
un oyf der nakht bin ikh aheymgekumen,

371
00:24:50,259 --> 00:24:57,089
ober, me hot gezogt az me vil forn nokh Rusland. zogn zey, "varts, varts, varts, varts.

372
00:24:57,161 --> 00:25:01,139
me vet forn, ets vet forn durkh Varshe. nokh Rusland fort men oykh durkh Varshe."

373
00:25:01,481 --> 00:25:05,644
dervayl iz gekumen dortn arayn a froy,

374
00:25:05,835 --> 00:25:12,546
tsu mayne kuzine, un zi hot gezogt zi hot gezen vi di eltern

375
00:25:12,770 --> 00:25:17,457
mayne, hot zi gezen vi ale yidn nemt men aroys fun di HALA,

376
00:25:18,710 --> 00:25:21,255
un me firt zey in di vagonen arayn.

377
00:25:21,255 --> 00:25:23,498
oyfn, oyf di ban, oyf di tsug.

378
00:25:25,106 --> 00:25:28,358
zi hot es aleyn gezen. un shoyn.

379
00:25:33,645 --> 00:25:35,884
nu. se hot gedoyert,

380
00:25:37,188 --> 00:25:43,326
un undz ze'mir keseyder bay di kuzines. zey, zey haltn undz, zey viln undz nisht farlirn,

381
00:25:43,331 --> 00:25:45,621
nokh Rusland, me zol forn.

382
00:25:46,807 --> 00:25:54,076
un me krigt a yediye, efsher nokh tsvey vokhn,

383
00:25:54,502 --> 00:25:57,636
nisht keyn gantse, efsher vintsiker,

384
00:25:58,350 --> 00:26:03,931
az undzere eltern zenen in SANDOMIERZ!

385
00:26:05,083 --> 00:26:08,624
oy! undzere eltern zenen in SANDOMIERZ?

386
00:26:08,624 --> 00:26:12,589
fort men shoyn nisht nokh Rusland, men fort shoyn nisht nokh Varshe, men fort

387
00:26:12,589 --> 00:26:15,456
nokh SANDOMIERZ tsu undzere eltern!

388
00:26:17,334 --> 00:26:23,590
keyn yidn hobn nisht gekent forn., tsu fis tsu geyn iz vayt.

389
00:26:23,679 --> 00:26:28,433
ober far mir mit mayn bruder hot dos nisht ekzistirt.

390
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:31,757
undz ze'mir gevezn fraye.

391
00:26:32,218 --> 00:26:37,117
in in Lodzh bin ikh geganen

392
00:26:37,117 --> 00:26:40,836
oyf di PIOTRKOWSKA gas, vu yidn hobn nisht getort geyn,

393
00:26:42,157 --> 00:26:46,641
me hot farmakht, far yidn tor men nisht geyn.

394
00:26:48,468 --> 00:26:50,876
"di hintergasn kenen zey geyn!"

395
00:26:51,557 --> 00:26:54,659
mit opaskes, ober in, oyf di

396
00:26:54,659 --> 00:26:57,441
WIĘCKOWSKIEGO torn nisht geyn keyn yidn

397
00:26:57,817 --> 00:26:59,907
far dem zey trogn opaskes,

398
00:26:59,907 --> 00:27:02,031
ikh trog dokh nisht keyn opaske!

399
00:27:03,842 --> 00:27:09,017
di tateshi hot gezogt er gleybt zey nisht un nisht makhn dos vos zey zogn,

400
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:12,139
bin ikh yo geganen.

401
00:27:12,397 --> 00:27:17,083
un m'iz yo geforn nokh SANDOMIERZ, ikh mit mayn bruder.

402
00:27:17,375 --> 00:27:19,969
un dortn getrofn mayne eltern.

403
00:27:21,155 --> 00:27:23,276
vi azoy zey zenen gekumen

404
00:27:23,703 --> 00:27:25,723
hobn zey mir dernokh dertseylt.

405
00:27:25,998 --> 00:27:27,782
zol ikh zogn vayter?

406
00:27:29,998 --> 00:27:34,954
di yidn vos me hot oyfgezetst oyf di, oyf di tsug,

407
00:27:35,972 --> 00:27:43,038
yo, zenen geven di ershte vos di tsug iz gevorn banutst nokh di krig.

408
00:27:44,915 --> 00:27:48,353
ale brikn zenen gevezn oyfgerisn.

409
00:27:49,910 --> 00:27:53,215
di daytshn, ober di polyakn, ikh veys nisht,

410
00:27:53,215 --> 00:27:56,976
far dem, dos ershte, zikh tsu vern, tut men

411
00:27:57,015 --> 00:28:00,455
iberraysn di brikn zey zoln ni- kon nisht adurkh.

412
00:28:00,455 --> 00:28:08,636
haynt iz iz do flit men, ober do- densmolt ze'mir geforn, hot men di brikn...

413
00:28:08,861 --> 00:28:13,726
un keyn banen zenen nisht geganen az se iz nisht do keyn brikn.

414
00:28:13,726 --> 00:28:20,713
hot men di yidn aroyfgezetst oyf di TOWAROWE, TOWAROWE,

415
00:28:20,713 --> 00:28:24,803
zakhene, zakhene, nisht far mentshn, vagonen,

416
00:28:24,825 --> 00:28:28,296
nor far khayes, vagonen, hot men aroyfgezetst zey,

417
00:28:28,368 --> 00:28:31,839
un me hot zey ge-, iber di brikn

418
00:28:32,115 --> 00:28:35,873
di LOKOMOTYWA iz geblibn far di brik,

419
00:28:36,215 --> 00:28:45,257
un zi hot, di LOKOMOTYWA hot gegebn a shtup di di vagonen,

420
00:28:45,257 --> 00:28:48,287
un di vagonen, mitn groysn shtup,

421
00:28:48,287 --> 00:28:49,206
zenen zey

422
00:28:49,206 --> 00:28:53,254
ober zey zenen ariber di brik, yo ober neyn. ober zey veln araynfaln in vaser,

423
00:28:53,833 --> 00:28:56,595
iz vet di LOKOMOTYWA nisht forn.

424
00:28:56,685 --> 00:29:00,479
un az zey veln nisht araynfaln, vet di LOKOMOTYWA forn.

425
00:29:00,479 --> 00:29:03,533
un dernokh, az zey zenen nisht arayngefaln un zey zenen

426
00:29:03,533 --> 00:29:06,163
mitn groysn shtup ariber di brik,

427
00:29:06,354 --> 00:29:10,466
iz ersht gekumen der LOKOMOTYWA un zey zenen vayter geforn.

428
00:29:10,623 --> 00:29:12,299
durkh andere brikn.

429
00:29:12,299 --> 00:29:13,825
hot men zey gefirt

430
00:29:13,863 --> 00:29:19,842
azoy oyf a por brikn, zey veysn nisht sara brikn, sara vaser, zey zenen geven tsu...

431
00:29:19,842 --> 00:29:20,912
ober me hot zey

432
00:29:21,153 --> 00:29:26,078
geshtupt iber di brikn, di daytshn zenen aropgeganen, zey zenen nisht mitgeforn,

433
00:29:26,078 --> 00:29:28,913
nor di yidn zenen gezitsn in di vagonen.

434
00:29:29,709 --> 00:29:32,727
me vet do blaybn a minut un me vet geyn vayter.

